## Applications

The Hikvision POE Switch(DS-3E0326P-E) 24 Port Fast Ethernet Unmanaged is suitable for:

- Medium to large offices
- Industrial factories
- Warehouses
- Hospitals
- Shopping malls
- Educational institutions

