('52995047-e43d-4354-aa63-a16a6f80690b', 'en', '## Overview

The HIKVISION NVR 8CH DS-7108NI-Q1/8P/M(C) is designed to deliver dependable performance for applications requiring industrial-grade management. This product ensures safe and stable operations. This product is backed by comprehensive documentation and technical support from the manufacturer.

## Features

